<div class="content" name="FAX_TAPI_LINECOUNTRY_LISTW" uuid="a49a1eba-5cfb-4fec-848b-cf55a9e1c8e2"><p>The <b>FAX_TAPI_LINECOUNTRY_LISTW</b> data type defines the
structure that <b>FAX_GetCountryList</b> (section <a href="8619db79-4289-4563-b7fe-ad423b072622" data-linktype="relative-path">3.1.4.1.37</a>) can use to
return the list of countries/regions from TAPI. For more information about
TAPI, see <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=119989" data-linktype="external">[MSDN-TAPI2.2]</a>.
