country/region&#39;s data defined by a <b>FAX_TAPI_LINECOUNTRY_ENTRYW</b> (section <a href="554a23e4-7dc6-4ee0-81e7-e2e625a8df08" data-linktype="relative-path">2.2.50</a>) structure.</p><p>This data structure is custom marshaled as follows and uses
